A Django project to demo the creation of models and APIs in a meeting scheduler.

Env:
- Python 3.13.1
- DJango 6.0

Migrate:
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate

Run (on port 8000):
python manage.py runserver

Test:
python manage.py test
python manage.py test service

Reload data:
python manage.py dumpdata > data.json
# Remove all folders and files in migrations, create an empty __init__ folder. Then run these commands:
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py loaddata data.json

Create new app:
python manage.py startapp app_name

Access sqlite3 database:
sqlite3 db.sqlite3
